overview: Forest Ranger and singing cowboy, Rex Allen, attempts to save a camp for underprivileged boys with the help of "Alfalfa " Switzer who plays one of the boys.
tagline: BLAZING NEW TRAILS! HERE'S THAT SHARP-SHOOTIN' SON OF THE SAGE-BRUSH...THE ARIZONA COWBOY...BACK IN ANOTHER BIG ACTION THRILLER!
title: Redwood Forest Trail
